---
---

<section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Image -->
      <div class="relative">
        <img
          src="/images/documents-desk.jpg"
          alt="Messy desk with documents and calculator"
          class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Pain points -->
      <div>
        <p class="section-label mb-4">The problem</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-10">Sound familiar?</h2>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-amber/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">"Did you send that receipt yet?"</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">You spend 5-10 hours every week sending reminders and following up. Your clients mean well — they just forget.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-coral" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 7v10a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2h-6l-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">"I uploaded it to the portal... I think?"</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Client portals go unused. Emails get buried. Documents end up in the wrong folder — or nowhere at all.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-coral" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">"Tax filing is in 3 days..."</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Deadline week is chaos. Half your clients haven't sent their documents. You're working nights and weekends.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
